  "title": "Accounts cum HR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description :</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle full set of accounts including AP, AR, GL, and bank reconciliations</p></li><li><p>Perform month-end and year-end closing</p></li><li><p>Prepare financial statements, schedules, and management reports</p></li><li><p>Manage GST submission and ensure compliance with statutory requirements</p></li><li><p>Liaise with external auditors, tax agents, and banks</p></li><li><p>Monitor cash flow, prepare payments, and follow up on receivables</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper accounting records and documentation</p></li><li><p>Support onboarding/offboarding administrative procedures<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement :</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree or Diploma in Accounting or Finance, or equivalent.</p></li><li><p>Minimum 3 to 5 years of experience.<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tan Sin Yong (Stella)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124127</p>",
